It's a pretty professional place. Though the price is in my high-end range, I have to say the quality is pretty high at the same time.
The staff is careful and nice to both me and my hair. I also like the music taste of this place.

originalText.text: Got my hair done by King. He was super nice, friendly, transparent and informative about what could be done with my hair at this appointment (considering I let my roots grow out for 5 months). Loved the purple color and cut I left with. Props to him for being able to style and manage my thick, wavy hair ✨

originalText.text: I never leave reviews and although i got my hair done here awhile ago I think it’s important for me to share that you shouldn’t go here if you have curly/textured hair! I got my hair bleached and dyed pink which wasn’t even the right color… they did an okay job with the bleach although the whole experience was a bit nerve wrecking because they would say they would check on me in another 30 min then an hour would go by without anyone coming up to me. Keep in mind someone next to me had their hair falling out from bleach I feel so bad :( Anyways once they were done bleaching and coloring my hair they went to blow dry it and style it but remind you I have curly hair so of course it’s going to look frizzy if you just blow dry it. They kept saying to me “your hair is really frizzy” and I replied “oh yea it’s just naturally curly” and then not even a few moments later they were like “is your hair always this frizzy?” They made me feel insecure about my own hair texture and I feel like a lot of salons do not work with textured hair which is OKAY but can’t they just specify this!! I ended up just asking to leave without getting my hair styled bc I had already been there for like 6 hours and why would I stay longer when they were just constantly criticizing my hair texture.

originalText.text: LITERALLY AMAZING! I am recommending Double Q to everyone I know!!! I honestly wish I would have gone sooner rather than trying out other salons or coloring my hair myself. I came in with orange peekaboo hair that would not lighten anymore, but Matt was still able to give me the most beautiful finished product!! The team was so dedicated and even stayed after closing to make sure it was perfect. I could not be happier and I will definitely be back! Matt is literally a miracle worker!
